items.summary: Update the backend implementation of the `_initializeAccessControlWithSecret` call path so that when the provided secret token is missing/empty (e.g., production URL has no `caffeineAdminToken`), the call returns promptly and does not hang or block actor initialization.

Ensure that the backend initialization behavior for `_initializeAccessControlWithSecret` remains safe: invalid/empty secrets must not grant admin privileges and must not weaken existing authorization checks for normal operations.
